item.title: How to add a tele with an object; Safe zone + Wild Zone; Delete object
item.dc:creator: @A.E.M A.E.M.
item.description:
@A.E.M wrote:

to delete objects use this

makeGlobalObject(Xcoord, Ycoord, 6951, -1, 10);//Delete dont change any of that except x coord y coord

to make an object tele use this

case OBJECTID: //pbject tele teleportToX = Xcoord; teleportToY = Ycoord; break;

and finally to change the safe zone find “public boolean nonWild()” or "public boolean inSafezone() an add

|| (absX >=NWcoords && absX <=NEcoords&& absY >=BottemSouthcoord && absY <=topNorthcoord ) before your last )
